'''Jai Raventhorn''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Gender/Legends|female]] [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Commando/Legends|commando]]. In [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]] she led a Rebel team to [[Bevell Three]] to capture four [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] agents, but the mission was compromised: only Jai escaped. The four [[Infiltrators/Legends|Infiltrators]] commandos who died included [[Leong]]. As a propaganda measure rather than a reward, Jai was promoted to [[Master Sergeant/Legends|Master Sergeant]]. At one point, she was engaged to [[Krül]], but he perished before the couple could get married.

Two months after the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]] she was captured by [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces on [[Zelos II]]. After an interrogation she shared a prison cell with freelance [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenary]] [[Dirk Harkness]], with whose mercenary group, [[Black Curs]], she would eventually become affiliated to some degree. Her younger sister [[Morgan Q. Raventhorn]] was a [[Alliance Special Forces/Legends|Rebel SpecForce]] major who died in the Battle of Endor.

Jai owned a [[720 light freighter/Legends|Class 720 freighter]] called the ''[[Doomsayer]]''.

